main event: A witness reported seeing an unidentified flying object in Richmond, Indiana on March 29, 1968.
interesting points: The observer gave a very sketchy description of the UFO sighting.
Both the observer and the witness were sent Form 117s but neither returned a completed form as of May 28, 1968.
There was insufficient data for the Air Force to evaluate the sighting.
The object was described as reddish-brown in color and made no sound.
The object was observed for approximately 20 minutes before moving behind trees.
